    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                             全新更新！2025年7月 – 巫师疯狂世界现已开放！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/0dc9090dcb0ef67cf533102eadec683f.avif?t=1766804688\" width=800 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>走进阴森恐怖的逃离卡通王国世界——加入愿望单，关注更新，带来全新挑战、惊悚氛围和扭曲惊喜。[ /b][/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/8c11a13771ae05dc6cda6b6b1e8baf14.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逃离卡通王国</strong>是一款1至4人合作恐怖游戏。扮演被困在垂死游乐园中的吉祥物。探索。解谜。受苦。每个游乐设施都藏着秘密——也是你逃生的一部分。[ /p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/1c35418f0636cc5679ff0f9d074cbfe9.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/1c35418f0636cc5679ff0f9d074cbfe9.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/b3ec2e494202aa96a5f5102aa7d2cd33.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演公园中的吉祥物之一，他们现在为生存而战。在最多4人的合作冒险中携手合作，或者在单人模式中独自面对恐怖。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/3152f05dafa252654bfa24e50ac29963.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/3152f05dafa252654bfa24e50ac29963.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.poster.avif?t=1766804688\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.webm?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/2173b6adf997dfaab73a02c40bb1bbab.mp4?t=1766804688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越公园中曾经欢乐的游乐设施的扭曲版本，这些设施充满了险恶陷阱、畸形生物和令人毛骨悚然的惊喜。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras/1766052095c5f5a72e97d61c705be869.avif?t=1766804688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198360/extras_big/1766052095c5f5a72e97d61c705be869.avif?t=1766804688 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好面对恐怖并逃离公园的掌控了吗？游乐设施已复活，恐惧潜伏在每个角落。<strong>逃离卡通王国</strong>——噩梦的主舞台！</p><br></p></strong></p>",
